nhc_headline: ...HENRIETTE FORECAST TO REGAIN TROPICAL STORM STRENGTH LATER TODAY...
summary: ...HENRIETTE FORECAST TO REGAIN TROPICAL STORM STRENGTH LATER TODAY... As of 5:00 AM HST Sat Aug 09 the center of Henriette was located near 21.4, -146.8 with movement WNW at 14 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1009 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 35 mph.
